ion":2},"title":"Ibn Wahb on Character: Learning manners best type of knowledge","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 17, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Abdul Barr reported: Ibn Wahb, may Allah have mercy on him, said, \"What I learned from the manners of Malik was better than his knowledge.\" Source:\u00a0Ja\u0304mi' Baya\u0304n al-'Ilm 581 \u0639\u0646 \u0627\u0628\u0646 \u0639\u0628\u062f \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631 \u0642\u0627\u0644 \u0627\u0628\u0646 \u0648\u0647\u0628 \u0631\u062d\u0645\u0647 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647 \u0645\u064e\u0627 \u062a\u064e\u0639\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0645\u0652\u062a\u064f \u0645\u0650\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u062f\u064e\u0628\u0650 \u0645\u064e\u0627\u0644\u0650\u0643\u064d \u0623\u064e\u0641\u0652\u0636\u064e\u0644\u064e \u0645\u0650\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u0650\u0644\u0652\u0645\u0650\u0647\u0650 581 \u062c\u0627\u0645\u0639 \u0628\u064a\u0627\u0646\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":30060,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/05\/19\/malik-adab-duty-of-students\/","url_meta":{"origin":26680,"position":3},"title":"Malik on Adab: Duty of students to have good manners","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 19, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn 'Abdul Barr reported: Imam Malik ibn Anas, may Allah have mercy on him, said, \u201cSurely, it is the duty of a student of knowledge to behave with dignity, calm, and reverence, and to follow the narrations of those who came before him.\u201d Source: Ja\u0304mi\u2019 Baya\u0304n al-\u2018Ilm 1\/543 \u0639\u0646 \u0627\u0628\u0646\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":18222,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/02\/20\/seeking-knowledge-jihad\/","url_meta":{"origin":26680,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Jihad: Seeking knowledge is jihad in way of Allah","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 20, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas ibn Malik reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever goes out seeking knowledge is in the way of Allah until he returns.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 2647 Grade: Hasan (fair) according to Al-Tirmidhi \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0633\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0645\u064e\u0627\u0644\u0650\u0643\u064d \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":24920,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2017\/06\/01\/malik-never-stop-learning\/","url_meta":{"origin":26680,"position":5},"title":"Malik on Knowledge: Muslims should never stop learning","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 1, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Abdul Barr reported: Malik ibn Anas, may Allah have mercy on him, said, \u201cIt is not befitting for anyone with knowledge to give up learning.\u201d Source: Ja\u0304mi\u2019 Baya\u0304n al-\u2018Ilm 423 \u0639\u0646 \u0627\u0628\u0